topic.title: Truecaller database leak
topic.body:
Anyone know where I can find the truecaller database leaks or maybe those of other caller id apps?
It says here it was sold on the dark web. Even if its not from truecaller, its a huge list of names, addresses and phone numbers. 
https://www.bankinfosecurity.asia/researcher-data-leaked-for-300-million-truecaller-users-a-12519
